{"tid":2506264,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"cctvb新公廁賤閪關嘉敏6萬幾followers有幾多係買返黎？","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:41:33.000Z","uid":132986,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"716e491df72c264c8e978beed869a17069947f51","tid":2506264,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"4月12臭閪關嘉敏簽cctvb可以攞最低工資un屎忽既報導一出<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">[25?]26歲關嘉敏憑ViuTV《全民造星3》人氣急升月入數十萬 倒戈簽約TVB成為大台藝人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2485410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2485410</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n唔使24個鐘4月13號 followers人數由6.7萬跌到落6.6萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNTYdjxni5nutA5eeN9BPf45kNYVCj1x7fbUb5rAXiLwn?filename=jnBYT7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnBYT7B.png&h=cc60bbed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmarQch2bD4u1n2UArxZgNMwrtW88qqdS5zFjqh3y4ntTY?filename=517EDzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F517EDzi.png&h=276f9d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4月14   6.5萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfUmabB67kjZKopdivZRXecgVTSjGS9H6GRGFWQFUk7Xg?filename=faanBk6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfaanBk6.png&h=39d774c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有睇全民造星3既觀眾都知關閪敏為求出位<br />\n手段可以有幾那渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n見到鏡頭會扮喊衝去攬住比佢投票foul走既隊友<br />\n「快d la」強入陳柏宇ig live<br />\n係ig講足十幾廿日輸比陳嘉茵好唔抵<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">詳情請睇 <br />\n全民造星陰濕公廁賤閪 關嘉敏 卡文 @ Bingo 追擊區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2447723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2447723</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跌咁多followers<br />\n賤閪卡文一定好驚會唔會冇廣告商搵佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買followers咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過賤閪敏都好慘<br />\n當初好撚多打手幫你講好說話<br />\n到入左cctvb之後竟然零打手咁濟<br />\n係咪岩岩入cctvb未攞到幾毫子底薪請打手護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4月25號升到66.8k(冇cap)<br />\n4月26號再升到67.1k(冇cap)<br />\n4月27號今次有cap喇升到67.2k<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf9LLmdeahREf4zVLTKtjiFHMENJL7sC8ivdvp34BAgq1?filename=QcE35eR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcE35eR.png&h=b77bb46c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相隔2分鐘升到67.3k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRin1ji6ijhKathFXMReNb8vTdxiHDumZeta1kcctj987?filename=rU12BmB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU12BmB.png&h=94d6b304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好閪利呀關嘉敏 多左咁多假ac follow<br />\n搵佢賣廣告同倒錢落海有咩分別<br />\n接觸客戶類型：支那假ac?<br />\n<br />\n呢排佢應該冇乜show 冇廣告冇節目<br />\n都可以多咁撚多支那假ac follow<br />\n如果唔係買就應該143已經開始比佢接支那客<br />\n<br />\n岩岩再睇一睇67.5k<br />\n個臭閪窿比人屌到爛左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTb1FQDZNMeqE3KLQw1vLghsm9juQmk5y2qDsb7mNBNn7?filename=qTPcd8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTPcd8k.png&h=a359630a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a621f7512d844989233fbaf03b837d0bdb8ab9","tid":2506264,"uid":21526,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"呢個西女人係咁忠心簽入CCTVB嘅話<br />\n就唔好擺VIUTV啲事跡喺ig bio啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292b41e5f447e6112f1e22056b94347e6a0915ca","tid":2506264,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"好平架