 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有巴絲講過odiu pre round鬧支涓d說話<br />\n公廁閪文係其他報導講過<br />\n<br />\n只可以話精人出口笨人出手<br />\n公廁閪文陰陰濕濕係d濕鳩報導講但冇人睇<br />\nOdiu係個咁多人睇既節目單單打打<br />\n蠢得黎又令觀眾覺得佢黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT4JLfDQ6GNsbTQZRfRfJA6evTz8PktBc5Xm6jddQd4wk?filename=fqtAb5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqtAb5G.png&h=99383bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf7msHLi8kqPLGNyNR4RFNj9UdecL92a7d4D2L6QLQX9V?filename=eb2JkY2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feb2JkY2.png&h=b21987cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4c214b6a436c719a534ba6049da7883e703129f","tid":2506264,"uid":132986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"292b41e5f447e6112f1e22056b94347e6a0915ca","tid":2506264,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"好平架咋follower"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"呢d幾錢個？<br />\n[25?]26歲關嘉敏憑ViuTV《全民造星3》人氣急升月入數十萬 倒戈簽約TVB成為大台藝人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/sREEByX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/sREEByX</a><br />\n#126 回覆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV2dknHeTdZFMnd1TcSTXAPicn2zjAtCS4qi415wazzrB?filename=RrBNNFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrBNNFq.png&h=2189bd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZxUJMfJuMSXMPKAnda1oMiEKHr2vqyXyJ5zJvmQLgtMT?filename=fPEceks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfPEceks.png&h=ff6739cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1162eb3e45fdd45a19060c9f59c1ff914d1b146e","tid":2506264,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"df5de9242